### Instruction:

Write a program that determines if a string is a palindrome.

### Response:

```
public boolean isPalindrome(String s){
    if (s.length() == 0){
        return false;
    }
    if (s.length() == 1){
        return true;
    }
    for (int i = 0; i < s.length()/2; i++){
        if (s.charAt(i) != s.charAt(s.length()-i-1)){
            return false;
        }
    }
    return true;
}
```

